How to use encoder_decoder.py:

./encode_decoder message.txt Key.csv LetterValues.csv encode 

encodes a secret message in a one time pad using the Key given in csv and the values according to
LetterValues csv

./encoder_decoder cipher.txt Key.csv LetterValues.csv decode 

decodes a cipher text file. 
